But `filter (flip all ok) ps` is `filter (flip all ok) (List.foldr ... as)`, which by the induction hypothesis is `List.foldr (concatMap ∘ okextendl) [[]] as`.

Thus:
`filter (flip all ok) (concatMap (extendl a) ps) = concatMap (okextendl a) (List.foldr (concatMap ∘ okextendl) [[]] as)`.

But the right side is exactly `List.foldr (concatMap ∘ okextendl) [[]] (a :: as)` because:
